                </div>

                <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane " id="home">
                    <div class="jumbotron">
                        <h2>Welcome <span class="small-font capitalize">@Session["Username"]</span></h2>
                        <p>We are ontdeals, We provide the Best deals Online and update them better than most other Coupon and Deal sites.</p>
